### Phase 8 — Admin: audit viewer & user list smoke tests (BR-8, PM-only)
### Prereqs: backend on http://localhost:8080 with seeded users (pm/ba/emp).
### Run top-to-bottom in IntelliJ or VSCode REST Client; tokens are captured via response handlers.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. PM login
# @name pmLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "pm", "password": "pmPass1!"}

> {% client.global.set("pmToken", response.body.token); %}

### 2. BA login
# @name baLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "ba", "password": "baPass1!"}

> {% client.global.set("baToken", response.body.token); %}

### 3. EMPLOYEE login
# @name empLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "emp", "password": "empPass1!"}

> {% client.global.set("empToken", response.body.token); %}

### 4. PM — audit log: full list (paged, default size 20, sorted createdAt DESC) → 200
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 5. PM — audit log: filter by entityType=Goal → 200, only Goal rows
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit?entityType=Goal
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 6. PM — audit log: filter by performedBy=pm → 200, only pm-authored rows
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit?performedBy=pm
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 7. PM — audit log: filter by entityId (takes id from a row above) → 200
### Replace {id} manually with an entity_id from step 5/6 response.
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit?entityId={id}
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 8. PM — audit log: time-range filter (last 24h) → 200
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit?from=2026-04-21T00:00:00Z&to=2026-04-23T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 9. PM — audit log: pagination page=0&size=5 → 200, content.length ≤ 5
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 10. PM — audit log: combined filter entityType=Goal & performedBy=pm → 200
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit?entityType=Goal&performedBy=pm
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 11. BA — audit log: blocked by @PreAuthorize → 403
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{baToken}}

### 12. EMPLOYEE — audit log: blocked by @PreAuthorize → 403
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}

### 13. Anonymous — audit log: no bearer → 401
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit

### 14. PM — user list: all active users (3 seeded) → 200
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 15. PM — user list filtered by role EMPLOYEE → 200, 1 row (emp)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users?role=EMPLOYEE
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 16. PM — user list filtered by role BUSINESS_ANALYST → 200, 1 row (ba)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users?role=BUSINESS_ANALYST
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 17. PM — user list filtered by role PROJECT_MANAGER → 200, 1 row (pm)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users?role=PROJECT_MANAGER
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 18. BA — user list: blocked by @PreAuthorize → 403
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{baToken}}

### 19. EMPLOYEE — user list: blocked by @PreAuthorize → 403
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}

### 20. Anonymous — user list: no bearer → 401
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users
